"setting" was being spelled as "settting" in ata-dma.c.
(Found by actually looking at my dmesg output!)
ata0: master: settting up UDMA2 mode on Aladdin chip OK

Fix: 

-Chris--PiTpfjgRxo1f9CgFFwleffgfPYvVtDNRUsoPtS3bwOcrfz2Y
